Ontology Specification Draft

Abstract

The PMD Core Ontology (PMDco) is a series of ontologis for representing knowledge that encompasses fundamental concepts from the domains of materials science and engineering (MSE). The PMDco has been designed as a mid-level ontology to establish a connection between specific MSE application ontologies and the domain neutral concepts found in established top-level ontologies. The primary goal of the PMDco is to promote interoperability between diverse MSE related domains. PMDco at GitHub: https://github.com/materialdigital/core-ontology
